{"tid":1569895,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"〔溫故知新〕同我入嚟，一分鐘同你講晒港中關係新仇舊恨","createTime":"2019-09-14T19:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T12:54:55.000Z","uid":77905,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9223925ab2edcf68da028e9a9956ec3e62a23b1c","tid":1569895,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:26:59.000Z","msg":"（趕嘅直接去圖）<br />\n是咁的<br />\n平時做得鍵盤戰士多，都少不免見到大量以下嘅comment同問題。<br />\n為咗大家回答以下問題時更有自信，同時又噏得到有關史實，<br />\n特意準備以下少又唔係好少多又唔算多嘅歷史。<br />\n<br />\n好喇，廢話唔多講，比較多遇到既問題係：<br />\n－點解今次示威會咁暴力？<br />\n－港英果陣就做狗，回歸中國就搞搞震？<br />\n－殖民地果陣都唔教中史，淨係英國佬洗腦，搞到個個反中亂港<br />\n－香港人點解唔認自己係中國人<br />\n<br />\n以上問題，可以係嚟自中立jj，藍絲，海外華人，唔知咩事既外國人。<br />\n回答以上問題嘅事實就係：<br />\n香港人回歸前好愛國，大家自認係中國人<br />\n回歸後反而無咁愛國，大家自認係香港人<br />\n原因係咩，可以睇一睇以下張圖<br />\n回歸前一直係補血，回歸後不停扣血<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaLNzm4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaLNzm4.png&h=593b0c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回歸前，香港一直擁有嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\"> 最好嘅中文同中國文化教育</span><br />\n令香港人以中國文化為自豪感，身份中華一份子而自豪<br />\n回歸後，香港政府有心重新洗牌 <span style=\"color: red;\">將文化教育 變成親政府教育</span><br />\n政策方面不斷挑戰香港核心，製造對立點<br />\n對立點亦由最初個別時件，發展到連帶教育、民生、到核心價值之上<br />\n對立點亦發生得越來越密集<br />\n將香港人由愛國一邊，推到對立一面<br />\n<br />\n至於點解好多藍絲同海外華人對運動反感<br />\n正正因為佢地既想像都係存在於 以中國文化為自豪感<br />\n簡單講就係時代差距<br />\n無視近二十年發生嘅事，政府無處理反而不停加火水嘅對立點<br />\n只要一日紅色三角形嘅問題未被解決<br />\n（好似而家又想重推國教，普選無期，150個日日有）<br />\n香港社會問題跟本無可能消除<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5c2ba080c861d8fb710730bac875b98d3b167e","tid":1569895,"uid":103098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfwAJn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfwAJn6.jpg&h=3e919e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hkqqk9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHkqqk9N.jpg&h=d9a5219b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8a9ce04b7002b944df3e2361169b1dee3e94774","tid":1569895,"uid":201992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:34:54.000Z","msg":"［重新整合有曬證據］朱植雄義士「被自殺」後再懷疑被黑警屈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569868</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4bd37ef4b3986524e9c1b0b88de0a4f6a8339def","tid":1569895,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:39:58.000Z","msg":"好多人仲未覺醒<br />\n<br />\n想香港好 一定要脫離中共統治"},{"pid":"f7321c96078fa98bcd287579be80c410c984be3d","tid":1569895,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T20:18:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7236cec0b2f3138970b60c62b19162a63ce7adea","tid":1569895,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T20:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf4b5dc8662b773a0f5e7ca44b34de16f01b838","tid":1569895,"uid":17199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T20:33:37.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"5b3da79cdc2d6dcac0d481317c39ab0f0883480b","tid":1569895,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T20:36:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救人真係好撚好撚緊要<br />\n<br />\n唔係前線先至可以救人<br />\n<ins>普通街坊 市民一樣可以救到人</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>守護孩子，全民救人！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgMhaTE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgMhaTE.png&h=b6a8bf6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推動全城街坊市民救人救手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568768</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36b0a17903bb9e7c