港人 香港好 完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:33:00.000Z","msg":"香港一步一步，由所謂殖民地壓迫<br />\n到後來華洋平等，自己一步一步行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n今時今日香港完全就係你所講<br />\n每件事都係支國搵盡著數<br />\n將愛國變成愛黨，反而更少人愛國<br />\n然後支國大義凜然行出嚟批評人唔愛國"},{"pid":"5411e49285c70085532791232b1edee7d71fcad9","tid":1569895,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4q9RNA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4q9RNA.png&h=15b8b704&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡體版！"},{"pid":"0c29b878efc7968eb005320edfce1cf844e5e76b","tid":1569895,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5411e49285c70085532791232b1edee7d71fcad9","tid":1569895,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4q9RNA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4q9RNA.png&h=15b8b704&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡體版！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3405b79867a4231db8188ec8e0f061367103d89a","tid":1569895,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c29b878efc7968eb005320edfce1cf844e5e76b","tid":1569895,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5411e49285c70085532791232b1edee7d71fcad9","tid":1569895,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4q9RNA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4q9RNA.png&h=15b8b704&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡體版！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:40:35.